  <div id="text-content_8313bfa2-8355-4549-ba93-bf6818758de2" class="text-block-content">
    <p>Add <a href="/t5/Instructor-Guide/How-do-I-add-or-edit-details-in-an-assignment/ta-p/971" target="_blank">details to the assignment</a>.</p>
  </div>
</div>
 
